headline: Coinbase, MicroStrategy Stocks Fall. Why It’s a Volatile Day for Crypto Shares.
summary: Coinbase Global Robinhood Markets  and other crypto-related stocks slipped early Tuesday as Bitcoin’s blistering rally appeared to take a pause. Coinbase  the crypto exchange, fell 2%, while the trading platform  Robinhood Markets  rose 1.6%.
